params.sqlcmd: "select " +" M_CUST.\\"CUST_CD\\", " +" M_CUST.\\"CUST_NAME\\", " +" M_CUST.\\"CUST_ANAME\\", " +" M_CUST.\\"CUST_KNAME\\", " +" M_CUST.\\"OWN_ORG_CD\\", " +" M_CUST.\\"OWN_PERSON_CD\\", " +" M_CUST.\\"CUR_CD\\", " +" M_CUST.\\"EXCH_TYP\\", " +" M_CUST.\\"TAX_CD\\", " +" M_CUST.\\"TAX_APPLY_TYP\\", " +" M_CUST.\\"TAX_CALC_TYP\\", " +" M_CUST.\\"UNCONFIRM_ODR_EFF_PRIOD\\", " +" M_CUST.\\"UNCONFIRM_ODR_EFF_TERM_FLG\\", " +" M_CUST.\\"PARTIAL_SHIP_INST_FLG\\", " +" M_CUST.\\"INSPC_ACPT_TYP\\", " +" M_CUST.\\"PRICE_ROUND_TYP\\", " +" M_CUST.\\"DETAIL_ROUND_TYP\\", " +" M_CUST.\\"EDI_CUST_VEND_CD\\", " +" M_CUST.\\"MODIFY_COUNT\\", " +" M_ORG.\\"ORG_NAME\\", " +" USER_MST.\\"USER_NAME\\", " +" M_CUR.\\"CUR_NAME\\", " +" M_TAX.\\"TAX_NAME\\" " +"from " +" M_CUST, " +" M_ORG, " +" USER_MST, " +" M_CUR, " +" M_TAX " +"where " +" M_CUST.OWN_ORG_CD = M_ORG.ORG_CD(+) " +" and M_CUST.OWN_PERSON_CD = USER_MST.USER_CD(+) " +" and M_CUST.CUR_CD = M_CUR.CUR_CD(+) " +" and M_CUST.TAX_CD = M_TAX.TAX_CD(+) " +" and M_CUST.COMPANY_CD = M_ORG.COMPANY_CD(+) " +" and M_CUST.\\"CUST_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_CUST.\\"COMPANY_CD\\" = ?"
"select " +" M_TAX.\\"TAX_CD\\" as \\"TAX_CD\\", " +" M_TAX.\\"TAX_NAME\\" as \\"TAX_NAME\\" " +"from " +" M_TAX " +"where " +" M_TAX.\\"TAX_CD\\" = ?"
"select " +" M_CUR.\\"CUR_CD\\" as \\"CUR_CD\\", " +" M_CUR.\\"CUR_NAME\\" as \\"CUR_NAME\\" " +"from " +" M_CUR " +"where " +" M_CUR.\\"CUR_CD\\" = ?"
"select " +" M_ORG.\\"ORG_CD\\" as \\"ORG_CD\\", " +" M_ORG.\\"ORG_NAME\\" as \\"ORG_NAME\\" " +"from " +" M_ORG " +"where " +" M_ORG.\\"ORG_CD\\" = ?"
"select " +" USER_MST.\\"USER_CD\\" as \\"USER_CD\\", " +" USER_MST.\\"USER_NAME\\" as \\"USER_NAME\\" " +"from " +" USER_MST " +"where " +" USER_MST.\\"USER_CD\\" = ?"

"SELECT " +" M_CUST_STL_CTRL.\\"BILL_ADDRESSEE_CD\\" AS \\"BILL_ADDRESSEE_CD\\" " +"FROM " +" M_CUST_STL_CTRL " +"WHERE " +" M_CUST_STL_CTRL.\\"COMPANY_CD\\" = ? " +" AND M_CUST_STL_CTRL.\\"BILL_ADDRESSEE_CD\\" = ?"
